https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NETBEANS-4970

Before:
```php
<?php

function test(): callable {
    return function ($test): void {
                echo "test";
            };
}
```

After
```php
<?php

function test(): callable {
    return function ($test): void {
        echo "test";
    };
}
```
